message: I think I'd like to see meeting feedback posted here. I'd also like to see meeting suggestions. And while we're at it: is this a better alternative to the Google Group/Mailing List?
Can we also use Convore for the back-and-forth with past, present, and future speakers? I say, "Why not?"
Last meeting on Compass and Sass was informative.  I plan on getting into this on a small project soon.
